{"tid":1919734,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[11/3新開] FiveM GTARP Server 招人","createTime":"2020-03-11T03:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:01.000Z","uid":351581,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91f076057c52a46addf85eda1c6bad04eba044c6","tid":1919734,"uid":351581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/cs8VSFS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Fcs8VSFS&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=2054dd5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/cs8VSFS</a><br />\n<br />\n事源係半年前左右上youtube睇到RP server的影片 之後開始接觸RP 半年間玩過唔少伺服器 可惜經常遇到不公 碰巧有一個小弟玩開的SERVER唔做賣檔 畀我以一個優惠的價格買斷了他的檔案 再找回以前一些比較熟的玩家開了個新server 廢話唔再多講 講下伺服器特色先：<br />\n<br />\n1: admin以前都在其他server捱過玩過 遇上各種不公平的事 因此在處理爭議時會從多方面出發 不會偏心<br />\n<br />\n2: 伺服器檔案方面經過優化後 中階電腦可以有45-60Fps左右 可惜到大型地圖及燈光密集的地方時仍會跌FPS<br />\n<br />\n3: 獨家插件 公寓(酒店)和物業系統<br />\n玩家可以選擇租酒店或購買物業 但由於物業會登記個人名下 因此登記人犯罪時有機會被帶回搜屋 酒店則不會發生以下情況 但是個人物業可以自己放置傢俬 創造獨一無二的家居<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686991002493517849/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686991002493517849%2Funknown.png&h=4eaf2b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686991075516350465/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686991075516350465%2Funknown.png&h=0f2022a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4: 各種地圖幫助你投入角色扮演 例如有法院，警局，醫院等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686991269204852761/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686991269204852761%2Funknown.png&h=7247635c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686991365980291117/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686991365980291117%2Funknown.png&h=d15ffe82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686992184435933193/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686992184435933193%2Funknown.png&h=8972cb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5: 多樣的職業和賺錢方法 (Discord內有詳細攻略 不用白名單都可以睇到內容 有興趣可以入Discord睇下 再决定留唔留低)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686992558404010041/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686992558404010041%2Funknown.png&h=6f147326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6: 作為香港的伺服器 當然要加返少少香港特色啦 我地特別加入區旗，香港緊急車輛，香港路牌等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686993064937783312/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686993064937783312%2Funknown.png&h=34d3f129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686993696327204873/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686993696327204873%2Funknown.png&h=ab0e4967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7: 接近200台模組車 持續增加中 大量日本車 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687137463181115402/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687137463181115402%2Funknown.png&h=e0222da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/686994440879079435/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F686994440879079435%2Funknown.png&h=55215f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8:3個賽車地圖 畀你挑戰汽車極限(秋明山, 紐柏林, 摩洛哥) 玩家可以在機場以傳送點自行前往賽車場 (自帶計時功能) 没有適合的車也不要緊 場内設有免費汽車借用服務<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687138674114166804/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687138674114166804%2Funknown.png&h=c0e83449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687139040264585243/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687139040264585243%2Funknown.png&h=6e6ad156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687139991369023513/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687139991369023513%2Funknown.png&h=decaef61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687140200102494238/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687140200102494238%2Funknown.png&h=f7a983e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/680401731997401108/687139712237830257/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F680401731997401108%2F687139712237830257%2Funknown.png&h=b4b97896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9: 伺服器已經封測了大約一星期 90%bug已經修復+95%中文化<br />\n<br />\n加入方法:<br />\n1. 加入Discord <a href=\"https://discord.gg/cs8VSFS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Fcs8VSFS&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=2054dd5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/cs8VSFS</a><br />\n2. 加入後會有Bot PM你白名單申請表 如果收不到的話可以在 Discord &quot;簽證申請區&quot; 中的釘選信息找到<br />\n3. 填妥表格後耐心等侍<br />\n4. 白名單審批後 可在 Discord &quot;伺服器IP&quot; 找到IP及加入遊戲的教學"},{"pid":"1290c460aaeda815f2741aebcfedacd50a0b35ef","tid":1919734,"uid":76450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"有一段時間冇玩RP 睇落好似幾正 玩完呢場lol入去睇下先！"},{"pid":"4dfb4cbf6529e935fe622e43c6ce2b2acc2e20cd","tid":1919734,"uid":351581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1290c460aaeda815f2741aebcfedacd50a0b35ef","tid":1919734,"uid":76450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"有一段時間冇玩RP 睇落好似幾正 玩完呢場lol入去睇下先！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"可以呀 歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072ef2b57c963bf9b30bd1dabe5e169cd62069f2","tid":1919734,"uid":76450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dfb4cbf6529e935fe622e43c6ce2b2acc2e20cd","tid":1919734,"uid":351581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1290c460aaeda815f2741aebcfedacd50a0b35ef","tid":1919734,"uid":76450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"有一段時間冇玩RP 睇落好似幾正 玩完呢場lol入去睇下先！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"可以呀 歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"我入唔到ser 係咪bug左?"},{"pid":"0477cea1bae8aa81bce29c665c70cc7e156e658a","tid":1919734,"uid":111648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:57:31.000Z","msg":"又係你你個濕尻肥仔hill 次次有人唔同意你就搵藉口踢曬d人之後就ban人然後又開新server 今次係第四個 如果我冇記錯？ 上一個叫日常都市 錢你又呃盡 共產黨 server <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b037c05111fce9b0c4d0bbdddaa71088d1c46df","tid":1919734,"uid":351581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"